# PYTHON AI CHATBOT BUILT ON TOP OF FLASK

# Python Version
## #############3.9.16 ###############

# How to use it
-Clone this projcet to your local PC
-Create a seperate python environment either on conda or other tool of your choice
-Install python 3.9.16
-Install All Libraries below
-Run your project 
-you will be connected to the PI http://127.0.0.1:5000/talktome

# How to use the API
-The API can be connected to a web App, mobile App, or on whatsapp

